|------|---------|
| `CssProperty` | Custom properties and standard CSS props set in `AttrMap` via `set_style()`. |
| `Direction` | LTR/RTL text direction for keyboard navigation. |
| `Bindable::controlled()`, `Bindable::uncontrolled()` | Factory methods to initialize controlled vs uncontrolled values. |
| `HasId` | Derive macro (auto-impl) that marks a struct as having a stable `id: String` field. |
| `IntlBackend` | Trait for locale-aware number/date formatting. Injected via `Env::intl_backend`. |

