597	## 2. Anatomy
598	
599	```text
600	SignaturePad
601	├── Root            (required)
602	├── Label           (required -- describes the signature area)
603	├── Canvas          (required -- the drawing surface)
604	├── Guide           (optional -- guide line or placeholder text)
605	├── ClearTrigger    (optional -- button to clear all strokes)
606	├── UndoTrigger     (optional -- button to undo the last stroke)
607	└── HiddenInput     (optional -- for form submission, value = SVG path data)
608	```
609	
610	| Part         | Element    | Key Attributes                                                    |
611	| ------------ | ---------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------- |
612	| Root         | `<div>`    | `data-ars-state`, `data-ars-disabled`, `data-ars-readonly`        |
613	| Label        | `<label>`  | Labels the canvas area                                            |
614	| Canvas       | `<canvas>` | `role="application"` or `"img"`, `tabindex="0"`, `ars-touch-none` |
615	| Guide        | `<div>`    | Hidden when strokes are present                                   |
616	| ClearTrigger | `<button>` | `aria-label="Clear signature"`, disabled when empty               |
617	| UndoTrigger  | `<button>` | `aria-label="Undo last stroke"`, disabled when empty              |
618	| HiddenInput  | `<input>`  | `type="hidden"`, `name`, `value` (SVG path data)                  |
619	
620	## 3. Accessibility
621	
622	### 3.1 ARIA Roles, States, and Properties
623	
624	| Attribute                | Element      | Value                                       |
625	| ------------------------ | ------------ | ------------------------------------------- |
626	| `role="application"`     | Canvas       | Custom interaction model (when interactive) |
627	| `role="img"`             | Canvas       | Visual content (when disabled/readonly)     |
628	| `aria-label`             | Canvas       | From `messages.canvas_label`                |
629	| `aria-labelledby`        | Canvas       | Label element ID                            |
630	| `aria-disabled="true"`   | Canvas       | When disabled                               |
631	| `aria-readonly="true"`   | Canvas       | When read-only                              |
632	| `aria-label`             | ClearTrigger | From `messages.clear_label`                 |
633	| `aria-label`             | UndoTrigger  | From `messages.undo_label`                  |
634	| `tabindex="0"`           | Canvas       | Keyboard focusable                          |
635	| `data-ars-focus-visible` | Canvas       | When focused via keyboard                   |
636	
637	### 3.2 Keyboard Interaction
638	
639	The canvas uses `role="application"` which opts out of standard screen reader virtual
640	cursor interaction, allowing direct pointer/touch capture. The ClearTrigger and
641	UndoTrigger buttons are standard focusable buttons reachable via Tab.
642	
643	### 3.3 Screen Reader Announcements
644	
645	The `SignaturePad` includes a visually-hidden live region (`aria-live="polite"`) that announces state changes:
646	
647	- "Signature provided" -- after drawing ends (pointer up after strokes)
648	- "Signature cleared" -- after clear action
649	
650	## 4. Internationalization
651	
652	### 4.1 Messages
653	
654	```rust
655	/// The messages for the `SignaturePad` component.
656	#[derive(Clone, Debug)]
657	pub struct Messages {
658	    /// Accessible label for the canvas.
659	    pub canvas_label: MessageFn<dyn Fn(&Locale) -> String + Send + Sync>,
660	    /// Accessible label for the clear button.
661	    pub clear_label: MessageFn<dyn Fn(&Locale) -> String + Send + Sync>,
662	    /// Accessible label for the undo button.
663	    pub undo_label: MessageFn<dyn Fn(&Locale) -> String + Send + Sync>,
664	    /// Screen reader announcement when signature is provided.
665	    pub signature_provided: MessageFn<dyn Fn(&Locale) -> String + Send + Sync>,
666	    /// Screen reader announcement when signature is cleared.
667	    pub signature_cleared: MessageFn<dyn Fn(&Locale) -> String + Send + Sync>,
668	    /// Guide placeholder text.
669	    pub guide_text: MessageFn<dyn Fn(&Locale) -> String + Send + Sync>,
670	}
671	
672	impl Default for Messages {
673	    fn default() -> Self {
674	        Self {
675	            canvas_label: MessageFn::static_str("Signature pad"),
676	            clear_label: MessageFn::static_str("Clear signature"),
677	            undo_label: MessageFn::static_str("Undo last stroke"),
678	            signature_provided: MessageFn::static_str("Signature provided"),
679	            signature_cleared: MessageFn::static_str("Signature cleared"),
680	            guide_text: MessageFn::static_str("Sign here"),
681	        }
682	    }
683	}
684	
685	impl ComponentMessages for Messages {}
686	```
687	
688	| Key                                | Default (en-US)        | Purpose                    |
689	| ---------------------------------- | ---------------------- | -------------------------- |
690	| `signature_pad.canvas_label`       | `"Signature pad"`      | Canvas aria-label          |
691	| `signature_pad.clear_label`        | `"Clear signature"`    | Clear button label         |
692	| `signature_pad.undo_label`         | `"Undo last stroke"`   | Undo button label          |
693	| `signature_pad.guide_text`         | `"Sign here"`          | Guide placeholder          |
694	| `signature_pad.signature_provided` | `"Signature provided"` | Screen reader announcement |
695	| `signature_pad.signature_cleared`  | `"Signature cleared"`  | Screen reader announcement |
696	
697	RTL: Canvas drawing is direction-agnostic (pointer coordinates are absolute).
698	The layout of Clear/Undo buttons and Label reverses in RTL.
699	
700	## 5. Library Parity
701	
702	> Compared against: Ark UI (`SignaturePad`).
703	
704	### 5.1 Props
705	
706	| Feature                | ars-ui                          | Ark UI                     | Notes                                                    |
707	| ---------------------- | ------------------------------- | -------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------- |
708	| `data` / `defaultData` | `data` / `default_data`         | `paths` / `defaultPaths`   | Equivalent (ars-ui uses richer `SignatureData` type)     |
709	| `disabled`             | `disabled`                      | `disabled`                 | Equivalent                                               |
710	| `readOnly`             | `readonly`                      | `readOnly`                 | Equivalent                                               |
711	| `required`             | --                              | `required`                 | Ark-only; form-level concern                             |
712	| `penColor`             | `pen_color`                     | `drawing.size`             | ars-ui has explicit pen color                            |
713	| `penWidth`             | `pen_width`                     | `drawing.size`             | Equivalent                                               |
714	| `simulatePressure`     | (via `SignaturePoint.pressure`) | `drawing.simulatePressure` | ars-ui records real pressure; simulation is adapter-side |
715	| `minDistance`          | `min_distance`                  | --                         | ars-ui has distance threshold                            |
716	| `name`                 | `name`                          | `name`                     | Equivalent                                               |
717	| `translations`         | `messages`                      | `translations`             | Equivalent                                               |
718	
719	**Gaps:** None.
720	
721	### 5.2 Anatomy
722	
723	| Part         | ars-ui         | Ark UI          | Notes                                                 |
724	| ------------ | -------------- | --------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- |
725	| Root         | `Root`         | `Root`          | Equivalent                                            |
726	| Label        | `Label`        | `Label`         | Equivalent                                            |
727	| Canvas       | `Canvas`       | `Segment` (SVG) | Different rendering: ars-ui uses canvas, Ark uses SVG |
728	| ClearTrigger | `ClearTrigger` | `ClearTrigger`  | Equivalent                                            |
729	| UndoTrigger  | `UndoTrigger`  | --              | ars-ui has undo                                       |
730	| Guide        | `Guide`        | `Guide`         | Equivalent                                            |
731	| HiddenInput  | `HiddenInput`  | `HiddenInput`   | Equivalent                                            |
732	| Control      | --             | `Control`       | Ark has wrapper part                                  |
733	
734	**Gaps:** None. Ark's `Control` is a layout wrapper.
735	
736	### 5.3 Events
737	
738	| Callback | ars-ui                      | Ark UI      | Notes      |
739	| -------- | --------------------------- | ----------- | ---------- |
740	| Draw     | `Event::DrawStart/Move/End` | `onDraw`    | Equivalent |
741	| Draw end | `Event::DrawEnd`            | `onDrawEnd` | Equivalent |
742	
743	**Gaps:** None.
744	
745	### 5.4 Features
746	
747	| Feature              | ars-ui                                  | Ark UI               |
748	| -------------------- | --------------------------------------- | -------------------- |
749	| Stroke capture       | Yes (full path data with pressure/time) | Yes (SVG paths)      |
750	| Undo last stroke     | Yes                                     | No                   |
751	| Clear all            | Yes                                     | Yes                  |
752	| Export to SVG        | Yes                                     | Yes (via getDataUrl) |
753	| Export to PNG/JPEG   | Yes (adapter-side)                      | Yes (via getDataUrl) |
754	| Pressure sensitivity | Yes (recorded per point)                | Yes (simulated)      |
755	| Read-only display    | Yes                                     | Yes                  |
756	| Form submission      | Yes (SVG path data)                     | Yes                  |
757	| SR announcements     | Yes (signature provided/cleared)        | No                   |
758	
759	**Gaps:** None. ars-ui exceeds Ark UI with undo support and richer data model.
760	
761	### 5.5 Summary
762	
763	- **Overall:** Full parity, with additional features.
764	- **Divergences:** ars-ui uses `<canvas>` rendering with `SignatureData` (rich point data with pressure/time); Ark uses `<svg>` with SVG path strings. ars-ui has undo support.
765	- **Recommended additions:** None.
766

